ZH: 她的书写很漂亮。
EN: Her handwriting is very beautiful.

ZH: 我喜欢用钢笔进行书写。
EN: I like to write with a fountain pen.

ZH: 孩子们正在学习正确的书写姿势。
EN: The children are learning the correct posture for writing.

ZH: 他的书写速度很快。
EN: His writing speed is very fast.

ZH: 请用黑色墨水书写。
EN: Please write in black ink.

ZH: 这本书写得非常工整。
EN: This book is written very neatly.

ZH: 她用毛笔书写了一封信。
EN: She wrote a letter with a brush pen.

ZH: 请在空格处书写你的名字。
EN: Please write your name in the blank space.

ZH: 我的汉字书写不太好。
EN: My Chinese character writing is not very good.

ZH: 他的书写习惯很不规范。
EN: His writing habits are not very standardized.

ZH: 老师检查了我的书写作业。
EN: The teacher checked my writing homework.

ZH: 请用规范的书写格式填写表格。
EN: Please fill in the form using the correct formatting.

ZH: 我很注意字迹工整的书写。
EN: I pay a lot of attention to writing neatly.

ZH: 她用钢笔的书写很有特点。
EN: Her writing with a fountain pen is very distinctive.

ZH: 学生们在课堂上学习汉字书写。
EN: The students are learning Chinese character writing in class.

ZH: 我们要求学生用铅笔书写。
EN: We require students to write in pencil.

ZH: 请认真检查你的书写是否错误。
EN: Please carefully check if there are any errors in your writing.

ZH: 她的学习笔记书写整洁有序。
EN: Her study notes are written neatly and orderly.

ZH: 我们要提高汉字书写的速度。
EN: We need to improve the speed of writing Chinese characters.

ZH: 老师会根据书写评分。
EN: The teacher will grade based on handwriting.
